---
import { ArrowLeft, Database, Globe2, ShieldCheck } from "lucide-react";
import BaseLayout from "@/src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const apiBase = process.env.OPHIM_BASE_URL || "https://ophim1.com";
---

<BaseLayout title="Cai dat - Bluesia Cinema">
  <header class="sticky top-0 z-40 flex items-center gap-3 border-b border-white/5 bg-[#07090f]/90 px-4 py-4 backdrop-blur-xl">
    <a href="/" class="grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-full bg-white/10 text-white"><ArrowLeft className="h-5 w-5" /></a>
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-black">Cai dat</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">Thong tin trien khai Cloudflare Free.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="grid gap-4 px-4 pt-6">
    <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white/5 p-5 ring-1 ring-white/10">
      <div class="mb-3 flex items-center gap-3 text-gold"><Globe2 className="h-6 w-6" /><h2 class="text-lg font-black text-white">Truy cap</h2></div>
      <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-zinc-300">App dang mo khong can dang nhap.</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-zinc-400">Domain san xuat giu nguyen <code>film.bluesia.net</code>. Khong dat route proxy video qua app.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white/5 p-5 ring-1 ring-white/10">
      <div class="mb-3 flex items-center gap-3 text-gold"><Database className="h-6 w-6" /><h2 class="text-lg font-black text-white">Nguon du lieu</h2></div>
      <p class="break-all text-sm leading-6 text-zinc-300">{apiBase}</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-zinc-400">Danh sach, tim kiem, chi tiet va tap phim di qua proxy metadata noi bo <code>/api/ophim/*</code>. Metadata va anh co the duoc cache tren Cloudflare trong gioi han 500 MiB.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white/5 p-5 ring-1 ring-white/10">
      <div class="mb-3 flex items-center gap-3 text-red-500"><ShieldCheck className="h-6 w-6" /><h2 class="text-lg font-black text-white">Mien tru trach nhiem</h2></div>
      <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-zinc-400">Ung dung nay chi proxy metadata va toi uu anh. Chung toi khong luu tru, phan phoi hay so huu bat ky tep video nao tren may chu rieng. Noi dung phim den tu nguon du lieu ben thu ba.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
